*vdr-1.2.1 (26 Jun 2003)
  26 Jun 2003; H.Ryll <henning.ryll@web.de>
  new version

*vdr-1.2.0 (04 Jun 2003)
  20 Jun 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  added AD3overDVB patch, contributed by trtr-z

  04 Jun 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  jumped to version 1.2.0, vdr now runs with uid vdr and gid video,
  pluginnames changed, some default dirs changed, added default
  plugins, moved plugindir to /usr/lib/vdr 
  added VDR_OPTS (vfat, rcu, akool) to steer the installation of
  patches and vdr addons
  added vdrshutdown.sh sample script

*vdr-1.1.31 (12 May 2003)
  12 May 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de> vdr-1.1.31.ebuild
  new version, version needs cvs head driver from 2002-05-10
  and is therefore marked unstable, nothing new

  15 May 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de> vdr-1.1.31.ebuild
  fixed compile problem (menu.c), see vdr ml

*vdr-1.1.30 (06 May 2003)
  06 May 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de> vdr-1.1.30.ebuild
  new version, version needs cvs head driver from 2002-04-27
  and is therefore marked unstable, nothing new

